            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong>, <strong>honey </strong>and<strong> white wine vinegar </strong>in a large bowl</p><p>Add 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [2 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and mix everything together – this is your<strong> honey mustard dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
